 The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
 and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
 
+## [0.2.7] - 2026-05-27
+
+PATCH. User-facing correctness fix plus test tooling and docs; non-breaking. Under
+`0.x`, non-breaking changes increment the patch version. (Versions 0.2.1–0.2.6 were
+consumed by release tags now orphaned on commits lost to repeated workspace resets;
+per the no-overwrite / tag-conflict rules this release increments past them.)
+
+### Fixed
+
+- **Keyword table no longer hides ranking declines.** Rank drops previously rendered
+  the same `—` glyph as "no change," masking lost positions. Drops now render
+  `↓ N` in `text-danger`; gains stay `↑ N` in `text-success`; flat stays `—`.
+
+### Added
+
+- Pure, non-finite-safe `rankDelta()` / `formatRankDelta()` in
+  `src/features/rankings/rank.ts`.
+- `node --test` harness wired to `npm test` (via `tsx`) with unit coverage for
+  `rank.ts` and `format` helpers (`rank.test.ts`, `src/lib/format.test.ts`).
+- ADR-0001 (test-harness & pure-logic coverage), backlog brainstorm (Markdown +
+  JSON), and the moonshots-2026-05-21 planning set under `docs/`.
+
+### Changed
+
+- `KeywordTable` refactored to consume the `rank.ts` helpers.
+- README tech-stack refreshed to the 0.2.0 platform (Next.js 16 · React 19 ·
+  TypeScript 6 · Tailwind CSS 4).
+
